    "We compare RARO against several strong post-training baselines under the same dataset, training, and evaluation setup.",
    "Supervised Fine-Tuning (SFT).",
    "The SFT baseline trains the base models to directly maximizes the conditional log-likelihood of the expert answer given the question, representing the standard use of demonstration data.",
